  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the context of the Risk Management Plan (RMP), as requested from Addmedica by the EMEA, to
      collect information about long-term safety of Siklos® (hydroxycarbamide) when used in current
      practices for the prevention of symptomatic vaso-occlusive complications in patients with
      Sickle Cell Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
